JO  - Journal of the American Academy of Child and Adolescent Psychiatry
AB  - This randomized clinical trial compared stepped care with a single empirically validated CBT program in 281 anxious youth. The two approaches did not differ significantly on outcomes, while stepped care used less therapist time.
