JO  - Psychiatry Research
AB  - A pilot RCT in community mental health services found stepped care used less therapy time with similar clinical benefits and quality-adjusted life years versus treatment as usual. The abstract frames stepped care as promising, but the study was small and did not test a whole public-health system.
