DO  - 10.1016/j.invent.2023.100675
JO  - Internet Interventions
AB  - This preregistered noninferiority trial found stepped-care internet CBT was noninferior to therapist-guided internet CBT at 12 weeks and 9 months. It supports one stepped-care delivery variant, but not a complete integrated model spanning universal, targeted, and specialist tiers.
