UR  - https://www.nature.com/articles/srep29281.pdf
DO  - 10.1038/srep29281
JO  - Scientific Reports
AB  - This systematic review and meta-analysis included 10 randomized controlled trials of stepped-care prevention and treatment for depressive and/or anxiety disorders. It found stepped-care treatment outperformed care as usual for anxiety symptoms, but it still stops short of evaluating a complete universal→targeted→specialist care system in youth anxiety.
